    Follow ADRs strictly.
  </role>

  <goal>
    A working discard endpoint that cancels checkouts, marks versions as discarded,
    and returns the preview URL for the last committed version.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Discard allows users to cancel their edits and release the lock without
      committing a new version. The version record is kept for audit trail but
      marked as Discarded.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/DocumentCheckoutService.cs</file>
